title: Flare # 1-16 (Heroic Comics)
description:
Comics are not just for kids anymore! So says the blurb on the cover of the first three issues. Because nothing's more mature than a g-string swimsuit who butt-pose in each and every frame!

Three issues published by Hero Comics 1988-1989
Sixteen issues published by Heroic Publishing 1990-1994

A hilarious uneven run featuring not too subtle plagiarizings of more famous super heroes
